A.query:
select distinct language
from languages
where country in (
    select country
    from populations
    where sex_ratio = (select max(sex_ratio) from populations)
)
  and percentage > 50;

select distinct poverty
from economies
         inner join languages l on economies.country = l.country
where economies.country in (
    select languages.country
    from languages
    group by languages.country
    having count(*) = (
        select count(*)
        from languages
        group by languages.country
        order by count(*) desc
        limit 1
    )
    order by count(*) desc
)

select language
from languages
         left join populations p on languages.country = p.country and percentage >= 25
group by language
order by COALESCE(avg(adult), 0) desc, language;

select  code
from countries
order by area desc, name
limit 1 offset 14;

select  code
from countries
where area = (
    SELECT area
    from countries
    group by area
    order by area desc
    limit 1 offset 14
)
order by name
